    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Once the vegetables are softened, increase the heat to medium-high</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>to the pan with your <strong>dried oregano</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
