    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the <strong>drained linguine</strong>, <strong>smoky plant based 'Nduja butter</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> smoky plant-based 'Nduja' linguine</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash more starchy cooking water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
